</div>
</div>
</div>
', 'multiple_choice_single', '[{"correct": 0, "options": [{"content": "A. an administrator"}, {"content": "B. a doctor"}, {"content": "C. a friend"}], "question": "Edward heard about a type of mosquito net from"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"content": "A. China"}, {"content": "B. Japan"}, {"content": "C. Egypt"}], "question": "Edward believes that mosquito nets were first used in"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"content": "A. was first developed by a soldier"}, {"content": "B. made them potentially dangerous to users"}, {"content": "C. was made possible by modern textiles"}], "question": "Chemical treatment of mosquito nets in the mid-twentieth century"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"content": "A. are likely to find they have an unpleasant smell"}, {"content": "B. should avoid using them every night"}, {"content": "C. may have difficulty obtaining the necessary chemical"}], "question": "The owners of present-day nets"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"content": "A. remain effective for longer"}, {"content": "B. use a greater number of chemicals"}, {"content": "C. give protection against more types of insects"}], "question": "According to Edward, Olyset nets are better than other nets because they"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">SECTION 3: PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT (MOSQUITO NETS)</strong></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hello Edward. Sit down.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Thanks. I need some advice on my presentation about product development.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Right. Have you decided what to focus on?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Yes, the product I’ve chosen is a particular type of mosquito net.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Any reason for choosing that?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Hmm, I spent last summer travelling around Africa with a friend. He’s studying medicine, so when we were in a region where mosquitoes cause malaria, we visited a medical center.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Uh huh. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">(21) <span class=\"citation-621\">I chatted to an administrator [A]</span></strong></span><span class=\"citation-621 citation-end-621\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"> </span>while my friend talked to one of the doctors, and I found out they’ve had far fewer cases of malaria since these mosquito nets became available locally. That made me interested in the<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></span>m.</p>\n<div class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----></div>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-path-to-node=\"2\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hmm, okay. Mosquito nets have quite a long history, don’t they? I believe they’ve been used in Japan for centuries.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> That’s right, though apparently, Queen Cleopatra slept under one in <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"76\">(22) ancient Egypt [C]</strong></span>. That was probably where they were invented. And much later nets were used in China, so perhaps they were invented there independently.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Originally they were made of silk, but later cotton was used, and nowadays they’re mainly synthetic. <span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">It wasn’t until the middle of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>the 20th century</strong></span></span> that they developed nets treated with insecticides for use by the military.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> And that was a major step forward.<span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong> (23) </strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\">T</span>hey used an insecticide called DDT, but it was later found that this could be harmful to people as well as mosquitoes [B].</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hmm. Is that still a problem with modern nets?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Oh no, the chemicals used nowadays are safe, even if people sleep under them every night, and the nets work and they’re odor-free. But they have to be treated fairly often with the chemical, which the owners need to do themselves.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hmm, uh, presumably distribution of the chemical can be a problem in <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"76\">(24) remote areas [C]</strong>.</span> I mean, people may not be able to get hold of it easily.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> That’s right.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hmm, okay. Tell me about this net you’re going to talk about.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Hmm, well, the brand name is Olyset, <span class=\"citation-620 citation-end-620\">and the product was invented by a Japanese company. These nets are an improvement on the alternatives because the insecticide is contained inside the fibre and released gradually. It’s not coated on the outside as with ordinary nets, so the chemicals don’t have to be repl<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></span>aced.</p>\n<div class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----></div>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-path-to-node=\"2\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Right, and Olyset nets are also tougher and don’t tear as easily.<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">(25) They give protection for at least five yea</strong><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">rs [A]</strong>, compared with a year or two for other nets.</span></span></p>\n<hr>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> I thought I’d introduce my presentation by describing the background to the new product… the general context.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> You mean the business context, where the investment’s coming from and that sort of thing?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Hmm, well, I was thinking I’d talk first about insect-borne diseases, particularly malaria, and why there’s such an urgent need for new ways of fighting it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> I’ve got some statistics about the numbers of people worldwide who get the disease each year. I thought I’d show those. They’re quite staggering.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> I can imagine. It’s one of the world’s biggest health problems after all. It would also be useful if you could find some statistical information on <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"155\">(26) how malaria affects a country’s economic output</strong> <strong>[G] </strong>and present that too.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Hmm, OK. I’m sure I can find something. After that, I’ll talk about mosquito nets first—the historical development just briefly—and then I’ll introduce the Olyset mosquito net.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hmm, yes. Keep it simple. You could just present a bulleted list of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"75\">(27) its characteristics—the things that make it different from other types of net [D]</strong>—and talk that through.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Right. Then I thought I’d outline the production process.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Fine. Should I give some information about <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"50\">(28) where the money for the project has come from? There are lots of government and private sponsors [B]</strong>.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Hmm, definitely. That’s a very important aspect of any product development. Where are the nets being manufactured, by the way?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Oh, over half are made in Tanzania by a company called A to Z. They got an interest-free loan to buy in the necessary machinery.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Well, I’d say a bit about the company profile as well, and then present <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"79\">(29) figures about numbers of staff and the kinds of people they’re employing [A]</strong></span> on the Olyset project if you can find the details.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Hmm, OK. I haven’t included any information about marketing. I’ve got a lot of notes about it, but I’m not sure how to present them.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> I wouldn’t mention that if I were you. You’ve only got a short time for your presentation and you’ve got quite a lot of material here already. But you should provide <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"173\">(30) some figures about output. Have you found out from the company’s website how many nets they actually produce [F]?</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Edward:</strong> Yes, it’s over 30 million a year.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tutor:</strong> Hmm, right then. I’m not sure how to finish off. What do you think about including something on potential…</p>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('2e92679a-c670-4bca-a7fe-036c51c468b4', '045511de-bbc5-40e4-9b2f-38555b652c56', 'matching', 'Questions 26-30', NULL, '<div class="s-block-item s-repeatable-item s-block-sortable-item s-blog-post-section blog-section">
