<p> </p>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Hello, Bakewell Travel, how can I help?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Oh hello, my name is Sarah Carter. I wonder if you could tell me about the price of plane tickets to Dubai.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Our computers are down, so what I can do is take some details about you and your travel plans. Then, when everything’s okay again, I can call you back. Alright?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Okay then, right.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> So, some details first. Your name was Sarah Carter, wasn’t it?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> That’s right.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And can I take a contact phone?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"7\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q1) Number 07958 8472 22</span>.</strong> Now, I’ll probably need to get back to you on this. Shall I call you back tomorrow morning?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Uh, I work on Wednesdays. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"33\">(Q2) Can you call me back on Thursday before 12?</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Fine, okay. So Mrs. Carter, how many tickets will you need?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Three adults and four children. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"39\">(Q3) So seven all together.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Are all the children under the age of 14?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> They are, yes.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Which date do you wish to travel on?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Well, uh, we definitely need to be there for the 24th. So if we leave the UK on the 22nd, we’ll have time to… from the 23rd. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"134\">(Q4) So the 22nd of October. Not this month, next month… November.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Right. And I assume these are return tickets?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Yes, we want to fly back on the Tuesday. Is that the 25th or the 26th?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> It’s the 25th. So it’s going to be a short holiday?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"7\">(Q5) We’re going to a wedding, we’re not going for a holiday.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Oh, that’s nice. Now, do any travellers have any special requirements? You know, special assistance with mobility and that sort of thing?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Oh, um, well actually yes. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"34\">(Q6) My son’s allergic to cheese. It makes him really, really ill.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Fine. So as soon as I can, I’ll look into finding some tickets for you.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Now, I wonder if I could just ask you a couple of questions as part of our market research. Would you be happy to do that?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Will this take long?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Just a couple of minutes, that’s all.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Okay.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> So, how many foreign visits have you made in the last 12 months?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> About six, I suppose.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And where was your last foreign trip?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Well, I was in Egypt in May, <strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"36\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q7) then most recently India</span>.</strong> Oh, nice! Yes, I’m off for some IT training in Bangalore next month, actually.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And was that a vacation?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> I’d love to go back there for a holiday, <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"48\">(Q8) but it was for business this time.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And I presume you use the internet?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> I do, yes.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And so you’ve seen our website?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Yes, I had a look this morning actually.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"41\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Well, we had it redesigned a month ago, and we’re keen to get feedback on how our customers find it, so…</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"42\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Oh right. Uh, oh OK. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"28\">(Q9) Well, I have to say I found it terribly slow, so I just gave up and thought I’d give you a call.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"43\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"43\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Oh well, I’m sorry to hear that, but yes, it does happen sometimes. Um, would it be OK for us to email you with any promotional offers?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"44\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"44\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> I suppose so. Well, OK. Uh, my address is <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"44\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">(Q10) carter.s@speedtech.com.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"45\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"45\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Is that S-P-double E-D-T-E-C-H?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"46\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"46\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Sarah:</strong> Yes, that’s great.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"47\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"47\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And can I ask how you found out about Bakewell Travel?</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('dcdb5a14-e3e4-4117-99d0-ab2c145b0cb6', 'ec06c489-adf7-4f17-9cb0-d9057cf3d728', 'checkbox', 'Questions 13-14', '', '<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, A–E.</p>
<p>Which <strong>TWO </strong>activities will take place on the first afternoon and evening?</p>', 'multiple_choice', 'null', '[{"correct": false, "option_text": "costume making"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "a musical show"}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "an informal dance"}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "a talk on dance history"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "dancing tests"}]', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('14498f8e-63fd-4bbf-b41b-13fa7a9a25b4', 'f489b5de-d96d-4770-be15-286e322a2aff', 'radio', 'Questions 11–16', '', '<p>Choose the correct answer.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>THE MIDDLETOWN URBAN FARMING SCHEME (MUFS)</strong></p>', 'multiple_choice', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "university specialists"}, {"option_text": "business people"}, {"option_text": "town planners"}], "question": "Who founded the Middletown Urban Farming Scheme?"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "to encourage more efficient land use"}, {"option_text": "to help lessen CO2 emissions"}, {"option_text": "to improve people’s eating habits"}], "question": "What was the original reason for starting the MUFS?"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "schools"}, {"option_text": "companies."}, {"option_text": "community centres."}], "question": "For the coming year, the MUFS will focus on recruiting members from"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "practical gardening tips"}, {"option_text": "plant science"}, {"option_text": "location of local garden sites"}], "question": "What kind of information is available from members of the MUFS committee?"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "soil and compost"}, {"option_text": "containers for plants"}, {"option_text": "gardening tools"}], "question": "What are provided by the MUFS for the physically disabled?"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "its usefulness as an aid for teaching science"}, {"option_text": "its contribution to reducing costs of school meals"}, {"option_text": "its help in encouraging community pride among students"}], "question": "According to school teachers, what has been an unexpected advantage of the MUFS?"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Chris Butler:</strong> I’m Chris Butler, and I’m the chairperson of the Middletown Urban Farming Scheme, or MUFS for short—a highly successful program which encourages city dwellers to grow their own fruit and vegetables, to become “city farmers” if you will.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\">Who started MUFS? Well, the idea of urban farming has been around for quite a while, particularly among town planners. <strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"119\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q11) But it was actually a group of Middletown business people, including myself, who decided to create what became MUFS</span>.</strong> University agriculture specialists got involved later.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Now initially, the aim was not some eco-friendly goal of reducing CO2 emissions caused by the transport of food from farm to dinner plate. <strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"139\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q12) It was simply to maximize the utilization of the vacant or idle land that lies within the city</span>.</strong> Of course, later we realized that an additional benefit might be a healthier diet for local people.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\">Let me tell you a bit about the groups that have joined the scheme. We’ve got any number of schools involved and loads of corporate employees, so our message seems to have been well received there. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"198\">(Q13) But for next year, we’re going to concentrate on getting various community centres, like those for senior citizens, to join</strong></span>, because so far they’ve been somewhat slow to take up the scheme.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\">Now the core committee of the MUFS is a group of dedicated gardeners. They probably won’t be familiar with your specific plot of land—they’re mostly amateurs—but <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"162\">(Q14) they are the people who know the ins and outs of gardening. And they will be happy to sit down with any MUFS member and make some hands-on suggestions about gardening.</strong></span> But don’t expect them to know the answers to technical questions like the Latin names of plants.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\">The MUFS are keen to support members who are physically disabled. We’re looking at the possibility of providing specially adapted gardening tools on loan to members who can’t cope with regular tools—that’s not happening yet—but <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"228\">(Q15) we do have some window boxes as well as larger containers which we can distribute free of charge to these members</strong></span>, although they will have to provide their own soil and compost themselves.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\">I’m especially proud of the work we’ve done with the local schools, both grade school level and high schools. The teachers say that they knew the scheme would be of some practical use in science classes like biology. Despite the original hopes of some, the fruit and vegetable plots haven’t provided cheaper lunches for their students, but what they didn’t anticipate was the change in attitude that the scheme has created amongst their students. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"447\">(Q16) They say the students have become much more conscious of their surrounding environment; they want to keep it neat and tidy.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Chris Butler:</strong> Now, a number of local organizations and businesses provide our members with free goods and services. Let me go through some of them.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\">The city hospital, as you might expect, has to provide thousands of meals for its patients. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"92\">(Q17) So, the manager of its kitchen runs a course for our members on how to use vegetables in a huge variety of dishes.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\">The local government found it had a large glass building which the parks department used to start off flower seeds and young plants during the winter, and <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"155\">(Q18) they agreed to allow our members to use this free of charge to get their own little seedlings off to a good start.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\">Another thing:<span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"> <strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"15\">(Q19) the university has agreed that if members send them a sample of their soil, they will do a series of tests on it to indicate what kind of plants will grow best</strong></span> and what types of fertilizer and nutrients would be best to use.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\">And just to make sure our members know what’s good for them, <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"61\">(Q20) a supermarket is offering a series of classes on how to lose weight and stay healthy by having a sensible diet.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\">Now, let’s talk about the practicalities…</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('bab6ef78-7788-4457-a3bb-12d9a805ae23', 'f489b5de-d96d-4770-be15-286e322a2aff', 'matching', 'Questions 17–20', '', '<p>Choose <strong>FOUR </strong>correct answers, <strong>A-F</strong></p>', 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "summary", "summaryText": "<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>city hospital {B cooking lessons}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>local government {E use of a greenhouse}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>university {C advice on soil}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>supermarket {D eat-to-keep-fit course}</p>", "answerOptions": [{"optionText": "A fertilisers"}, {"optionText": "B cooking lessons"}, {"optionText": "C advice on soil"}, {"optionText": "D eat-to-keep-fit course"}, {"optionText": "E use of a greenhouse"}, {"optionText": "F market stalls"}], "matchingItems": []}', 'null', 'null', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('542c78e0-bcad-4bc2-862c-685c8ae6895f', '8a28e847-7c79-49ce-94e9-cf1ae900a7fc', 'radio', 'Questions 21–26', '', '<p>Choose the correct answer.</p>', 'multiple_choice', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "she has read it too."}, {"option_text": "what she says reminds him of it."}, {"option_text": "he thinks she might like to do similar research."}], "question": "Daniel mentions the research about walking and creativity to Katie because"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "sitting"}, {"option_text": "running"}, {"option_text": "listening to music."}], "question": "In the experiments, researchers compared participants’ creativity when walking and when"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "type of control group."}, {"option_text": "pattern of activities."}, {"option_text": "way of selecting participants."}], "question": "Daniel says that in each experiment, there was a different"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "biased in favour of certain people"}, {"option_text": "a good indicator of creativity."}, {"option_text": "open to personal interpretation."}], "question": "Daniel thinks the experiment with words is"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "they are doubtful about its aims."}, {"option_text": "they are confused by its methods."}, {"option_text": "they are cautious about its conclusions."}], "question": "What is Katie and Daniels attitude to the experiment on focused thinking?"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "whether other types of exercise affect creativity."}, {"option_text": "the cause of the improvement in creativity."}, {"option_text": "how the results can be applied to creativity in real life."}], "question": "Katie thinks that the best way forward is to consider"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Hi Daniel!</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Katie, you look as if you’re off somewhere.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Yes, I was just heading out for a walk.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">(Q21) Hmm, funny. I was just reading an article about some research that’s been done on the effects of walking on creativity.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Huh, sounds interesting. I’ve always found walking helped me think, but this article confirms that everybody can benefit.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Oh, tell me more.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Okay, but I may even do some more research on it at some point, so don’t pinch my idea, promise? Well, in the experiments, the researchers tested participants’ creativity by comparing how many ideas they thought of while they were walking, compared to while they were doing other activities.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> What, like listening to music?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Nothing like that. <strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"26\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q22) But they did analyze the ideas participants came up with when sitting both outdoors and inside</span>.</strong> What I found surprising was that they didn’t compare walking to other forms of exercise, like running for example.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Right. So what was the difference between the experiments?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"7\">(Q23) Well, in each one, the activities were put together in different ways.</strong></span> Several of the experiments specifically focused on the ability of participants to come up with new ideas. Then the final experiment was a control test of sorts.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Oh, right.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> In one experiment, participants had to think of unusual uses for three everyday objects within a time limit.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> OK, and then there was an experiment with words. What did they ask them to do?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Compare words in unusual ways. For example, the word “sweet”. If participants simply said “sweet as sugar”, that wasn’t creative. But an answer like “sweet as a cat with honey on its paws” was okay.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> I can see why they’d ask them to do that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Really? I just don’t see how the experiment is fair.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Why?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Because the conclusions are based only on the researcher’s opinion.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">(Q24) I think it’s more that anyone who’d studied language would be at an advantage.</strong></span> Hmm, OK. Was there an experiment about focused thinking?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Yeah, there was. It aimed to find out if walking helped focused thinking, though I wasn’t sure that I agreed with their findings. They decided that walking doesn’t help this type of thinking.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> What evidence did they have?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Well, that’s it. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"24\">(Q25) I don’t think there was enough evidence to support their conclusions, even if their methods were sound.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Well, I’d certainly hesitate before making such a bold statement. Still, it’s a first step, isn’t it?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> I suppose to move forward with this, they’ll need to test other ways people keep fit, like swimming. That would be useful. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"130\">(Q26) But personally, I’d like to know more about the fundamental reason for the effect on people’s creativity.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> That would be good. Then it could be applied more widely in work, for example.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Again, that’s secondary, really.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> But how would you test walking if you wanted to assess its physical benefits?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Well, firstly, I’d like to know more about the benefits of different situations. What about the effect of footwear?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Hmm, hadn’t thought of that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Well, I’ve read that shoes with thinner soles were found to be better for people’s joints. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"98\">(Q27) It even made the skeletal structure tougher.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Interesting. Was that because they lost weight?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Not as far as I’m aware. And then there’s walking in the mountains.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Walking in the mountains? Hmm, I think I’ve read something about that. Doesn’t altitude help people regulate their sleep patterns?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"> <strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"7\">(Q28) It’s more that it improves your vision.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> It must be those breathtaking views.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"41\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Yeah. And what about the effect that walking has for elderly people? Better balance, by any chance?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"42\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> More than that. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"24\">(Q29) It had a positive effect by helping them maintain their body clock’s natural rhythm, both when going to bed and waking up.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"43\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"43\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Right. And what about the effect of walking long distances?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"44\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"44\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Daniel:</strong> Well, a person needs to find the balance between their optimum speed and their natural breathing pattern. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"44\" data-index-in-node=\"114\">(Q30) Once they’re synchronized, they can just keep on going for much longer periods than they could before.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"45\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"45\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Katie:</strong> Hmm, I can see how that would work. But anyway…</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('fe9aee14-057f-4255-9f5f-25c639772f36', '31e2014f-e2f4-4fda-bd57-7fc90434527c', 'radio', 'Questions 21–24', '', '<p>Choose the correct letter, <strong>A</strong>, <strong>B </strong>or <strong>C</strong>.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Presentation on African art</strong></span></p>', 'multiple_choice', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "A. He read several journal articles."}, {"option_text": "B. He attended an exhibition."}, {"option_text": "C. He spent some time in Nigeria."}], "question": "What first attracted Terence to the topic of Ife sculptures?"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "A. abstract designs."}, {"option_text": "B. fish and wild animals."}, {"option_text": "C. people."}], "question": "In his presentation Terence will focus on sculptures featuring"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "A. He received money from an arts organisation."}, {"option_text": "B. His mother and father paid for him."}, {"option_text": "C. He wrote about the trip for a newspaper."}], "question": "How did Terence finance his trip to Ife?"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "A. helping at an archaeological site"}, {"option_text": "B. the professor he met"}, {"option_text": "C. the artists he got to know"}], "question": "What was most memorable for Terence about his trip?"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-start=\"67\" data-end=\"235\">Tutor: Okay Terence, now I’ve looked through your preliminary outline and notes for the presentation on the art of the Ife region in Africa – that’s in Nigeria right?</p>\n<p data-start=\"237\" data-end=\"324\">Terence: Yes, I’m concentrating on life sculptures from the 12th to the 15th century.</p>\n<p data-start=\"326\" data-end=\"455\">Tutor: How did you get interested in that? I know there have been some recent articles in the journals about African sculpture.</p>\n<p data-start=\"457\" data-end=\"748\">Terence: Well I’ve read most of those now, but <strong><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(21) initially I got my introduction to this at a special display at the City Museum a few years ago</span></strong>. I just happened to be there and saw these works and thought they were fantastic, and I even went to Nigeria last summer to see more of them.</p>\n<p data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"894\">Tutor: I’ve seen the photos for your presentation and I must say the sculptures are gorgeous portrayals of what appear to be kings and Queens.</p>\n<p data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"1249\">Terence: <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(22) Yes I decided to concentrate on those as they’re the most typical</strong></span>. They’re interesting because they’re so naturalistic, unlike the abstract figures we often associate with African art. There’s also a lovely sculpture of a mudfish and one of the scaly crocodile, but I didn’t get very good pictures of those so I won’t spend long on them.</p>\n<p data-start=\"1251\" data-end=\"1361\">Tutor: Right. So what was the city of Ife like when these works were made? It’s on the Niger River isn’t it?</p>\n<p data-start=\"1363\" data-end=\"1523\">Terence: Yeah, the boat traffic’s what made it a center of commerce then as it still is today, but nowadays it’s better known as the home of a big university.</p>\n<p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1587\">Tutor: Speaking of modern day life, tell me about your trip.</p>\n<p data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1951\">Terence: Ha, I was incredibly lucky to be able to get enough money to go. My parents encouraged me but they couldn’t afford to send me. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(23) I applied for a grant from the Arts Council and in the end I got it</strong></span>. I also wrote a series of articles about my trip for the local newspaper but I didn’t get any money for that. I was just pleased to get them published.</p>\n<p data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"1992\">Tutor: And the highlight of the trip?</p>\n<p data-start=\"1994\" data-end=\"2350\">Terence: <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(24) That had to be meeting a professor working on the site in Ife</strong></span> who had been a young boy when they first discovered the sculptures by accident at a building site in 1938. He had been working at the site, of course I also got to talk to lots of artists who are working there today, and I got to try my hand at making a little sculpture myself.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2352\" data-end=\"2355\">\n<p data-start=\"2357\" data-end=\"2488\">Tutor: Well let’s see what you might do to improve what you’re planning for your presentation. About the sculptures themselves…</p>\n<p data-start=\"2490\" data-end=\"2708\">Terence: I think <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(25/26) I need to add as much as possible about the details of the way they were made</strong></span>. Of course, I can’t add anything about the artists who made them because nobody really knows anything about them.</p>\n<p data-start=\"2710\" data-end=\"2937\">Tutor: All good points, and you’ve certainly said enough about what the sculptures depict and what the subjects are, that’s well covered. But <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(25/26) I’d make some bigger photos of them so you can clearly see the fine detail</strong></span>.</p>\n<p data-start=\"2939\" data-end=\"3175\">Terence: Okay, and I would limit my personal reactions to these works of art if I were you. I know you think they’re fantastic. You’re right, I’ll contain my enthusiasm. What about the section of the presentation which I call history?</p>\n<p data-start=\"3177\" data-end=\"3349\">Terence: <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(27/28) I’d like to go into more depth about the history of that whole area, you know in the countries around Nigeria</strong></span>. That would make the presentation stronger.</p>\n<p data-start=\"3351\" data-end=\"3664\">Tutor: But I think you’ve covered the situation regarding the rulers of the country quite well and you’ve got plenty already about what the Ife people were doing then and the way their society was structured. And in fact I think you could cut out the bit about modern Nigerian history because it’s not relevant.</p>\n<p data-start=\"3666\" data-end=\"3853\">Terence: I agree that doesn’t fit, <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(27/28) but perhaps I should concentrate more on the religious beliefs</strong></span>, since all these sculptures do seem to have some kind of religious association.</p>\n<p data-start=\"3855\" data-end=\"4092\">Tutor: Good, I can lend you a book on that. Now, probably the part the class will find most interesting is the report of your trip to Nigeria and the research you did there. So I gather you managed to use the university library in Ife?</p>\n<p data-start=\"4094\" data-end=\"4547\">Terence: Yes, as soon as I had explained why I wanted the information, that was no problem; they couldn’t have been more helpful. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(29/30) There were some interesting accounts of how the first sculptures were found and what happened to them, which I want to include</strong></span>. What struck me when I saw the sculptures in Nigeria is the extent to which 20th century European artists were influenced by them, but that’s beyond the scope of my presentation I think.</p>\n<p data-start=\"4549\" data-end=\"4646\">Tutor: Yes. What about the sources of the materials they used? You don’t mention that anywhere.</p>\n<p data-start=\"4648\" data-end=\"4888\">Terence: <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(29/30) I didn’t manage to find out much about that</strong></span>. I want to cover <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>(29/30) the theories about who the original sculptors were though</strong></span>… the idea that a lot of them may have been made by the same person. That’s very interesting.</p>\n<p data-start=\"4890\" data-end=\"4982\">Tutor: It is, isn’t it? Right, well thanks for all the advice. Now I think I need to work.</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('3fc94a01-5549-4fed-a241-2636935d769e', '31e2014f-e2f4-4fda-bd57-7fc90434527c', 'checkbox', 'Questions 25-26', '', '<p data-start="903" data-end="929">Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, <strong>A</strong>–<strong>E</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="931" data-end="1021">Which <strong>TWO </strong>additions will Terence make to the part of the presentation on the sculptures?</p>', 'multiple_choice', 'null', '[{"correct": true, "option_text": "A. enlarged pictures of the sculptures"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "B. more material about the subjects"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "C. more about his personal opinion of the art works"}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "D. extra information about the techniques used"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "E. additional information about the artists"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('bc9c3b13-6362-40aa-a279-ee44fdc18c84', '31e2014f-e2f4-4fda-bd57-7fc90434527c', 'checkbox', 'Questions 27-28', '', '<p data-start="1287" data-end="1313">Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, <strong>A</strong>–<strong>E</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1315" data-end="1381">Which <strong>TWO </strong>additions will Terence make to the section on history?</p>', 'multiple_choice', 'null', '[{"correct": false, "option_text": "A. data about the kings in the Ife area"}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "B. extra information about the surrounding region"}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "C. examination of the beliefs of the Ife people"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "D. an explanation of the development of modern Ife"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "E. more details of past activities of the Ife people"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('2aa41d30-b058-4617-9323-4aec1aba9319', 'f99f53ba-caa7-413d-bffa-c8c408954ad9', 'checkbox', 'Questions 19–20', NULL, '<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>correct answers.</p>
<p>Which <strong>TWO </strong>things does Arthur say helped him get his business started?</p>', 'multiple_choice_many', 'null', '[{"option": "family support", "correct": true}, {"option": "getting a loan from a bank", "correct": true}, {"option": "good business advice", "correct": false}, {"option": "a favourable economic climate", "correct": false}, {"option": "an effective approach to business", "correct": false}]', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": ""}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('2a7f0138-62d7-48c2-bf53-3732239d8273', '8a28e847-7c79-49ce-94e9-cf1ae900a7fc', 'matching', 'Questions 27–30', '', '<p>What is the main physical benefit of each of the following walking situations?</p>
<p>Choose <strong>FOUR </strong>correct answers, <strong>A-G</strong>, next to questions <strong>27-30</strong>.</p>', 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "summary", "summaryText": "<p><strong>Walking situations</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>walking with thin-soled footwear {F stronger bones}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>walking in the mountains {C better eyesight}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>walking for the elderly {E regulate sleeping pattern}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>walking long distances {B greater stamina}</p>", "answerOptions": [{"optionText": "A improve balance"}, {"optionText": "B greater stamina"}, {"optionText": "C better eyesight"}, {"optionText": "D lower blood pressure"}, {"optionText": "E regulate sleeping pattern"}, {"optionText": "F stronger bones"}, {"optionText": "G weight reduction"}], "matchingItems": []}', 'null', 'null', 1);
SET session_replication_role = DEFAULT;
